reviewText:
I guess that I have only myself to blame.  I've bought so many Chinese videos at Amazon.com that I didn't give this a second thought.  I should've known that with almost no description, and that it was recorded on demand, that something was up.  In any case, can't blame Amazon.com, but they could provide more information, as well.

Basically, it's a subteen-level show... Really hokey.  NOT for Chinese movie buffs.
